                                                <Run FontWeight="SemiBold" Foreground="#FBBF24">SortList bug:</Run>  When SortList has exactly 1 item, the server calls GetPrimaryKey().First() which throws if the entity has no PK mapping. Always send 0 or 2+ sort items. The seeded collections already include a 2-item SortList workaround.
