                                        <TextBlock Grid.Column="1" FontSize="12" Foreground="{DynamicResource SubText}" TextWrapping="Wrap">.../BudgetsPageTotal — returns total page count for a given PageSize. Used to build pagination UI.</TextBlock>
                                    </Grid>
