                                        <TextBlock Grid.Column="1" FontSize="12" Foreground="{DynamicResource SubText}" TextWrapping="Wrap"><Run FontWeight="SemiBold" Foreground="{DynamicResource PrimaryText}">Pick a collection.</Run>  Expand the sidebar, click any request. The URL, method, body, and auth pre-fill automatically.</TextBlock>
