                                        <TextBlock Grid.Column="1" FontSize="12" Foreground="{DynamicResource SubText}" TextWrapping="Wrap"><Run FontWeight="SemiBold" Foreground="{DynamicResource PrimaryText}">Set auth.</Run>  Go to the Auth tab → Bearer Token → paste your token. Or use API Key with header name APIKEY.</TextBlock>
                                    </Grid>
                                    <Grid Margin="0,0,0,8"><Grid.ColumnDefinitions><ColumnDefinition Width="28"/><ColumnDefinition Width="*"/></Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                        <Border Width="20" Height="20" CornerRadius="10" Background="#7C3AED" VerticalAlignment="Top" Margin="0,1,0,0"><TextBlock Text="4" FontSize="10" FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="White" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center"/></Border>
                                        <TextBlock Grid.Column="1" FontSize="12" Foreground="{DynamicResource SubText}" TextWrapping="Wrap"><Run FontWeight="SemiBold" Foreground="{DynamicResource PrimaryText}">Click Send (▶).</Run>  Response appears in the panel below. Toggle Pretty/Raw. Headers are in the Headers tab.</TextBlock>
