                                        <TextBlock Grid.Column="1" FontSize="12" Foreground="{DynamicResource SubText}" TextWrapping="Wrap"><Run FontWeight="SemiBold" Foreground="{DynamicResource PrimaryText}">Recent history.</Run>  Every sent request is logged in the Recent panel (sidebar). Click any entry to reload it instantly.</TextBlock>
                                    </Grid>
